out_azure_bob: fix coroutine swap When Azure blob post is completed/failed, the socket FD should be removed from epoll monitor targets. However, there are paths which don't remove it which causes unwanted epoll trigger with bogus pointer of a coroutine swap target which leads to a crash. The fix is to clear it to avoid the crash.
